pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: A group of Daemonheim spiders are roaming near the border north of Ube's beacon, north-east of Varrock. An extermination attempt will begin soon.
name: Spider Swarm
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Spider Swarm has started north of Ube's beacon, north-east of Varrock!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Demonic forces are prospecting an outcrop of ore near the south Wilderness Runite mine. They will start mining it soon.
name: Unnatural Outcrop
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Unnatural Outcrop has started near the south Wilderness Runite mine!

name: Stryke the Wyrm
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Stryke the Wyrm has started near the south-east of the Lava Maze!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Demonic forces are summoning a new legion of demons in the Wilderness Crater. Daemonheim forces will reward their removal.
name: Demon Stragglers
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Demon Stragglers has started in the Wilderness Crater!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Demonic forces are tracking a group of rare butterflies. They will intercept them near the obelisk south of the Wilderness lodestone soon.
name: Butterfly Swarm
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Butterfly Swarm has started south of the Wilderness Lodestone!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: The King Black Dragon is infuriated by the disturbances in the Wilderness and is preparing to take out his rage on all combatants near Daemonheim.
name: King Black Dragon Rampage
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: King Black Dragon Rampage has started on the plain north-west of Daemonheim!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: A raiding party of forgotten soldiers are advancing on the plain near the Daemonheim peninsula. Demonic forces want them killed.
name: Forgotten Soldiers
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Forgotten Soldiers have arrived on the plain near the Daemonheim peninsula!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Daemonheim forces are analysing some new plants at a pond south of the Wilderness lodestone. They will start harvesting them soon.
name: Surprising Seedlings
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Surprising Seedlings has started at the pond south of the Wilderness lodestone!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: A pack of hellhounds is running to disrupt the Trollheim beacon, near the Dark Warriors' Fortress. Daemonheim forces need them killed.
name: Hellhound Pack
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Hellhound Pack has started near the Dark Warriors' Fortress!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: The Wilderness Volcano has launched a large rock high into the air above the wilderness. It will land soon near the Chaos Temple.
name: Infernal Star
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Infernal Star has started near the Chaos Temple!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Daemonheim forces are getting ready to collect ectoplasm from the Forgotten Cemetery.
name: Lost Souls
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Lost Souls has started in the Forgotten Cemetery!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: A ramokee squad has arrived to harass demons in the wilderness. They will rally soon by the shipwreck on the Daemonheim peninsula.
name: Ramokee Incursion
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Ramokee Incursion has started by the shipwreck on the Daemonheim peninsula!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Daemonheim forces have detected a spike in divine energy west of the Dark Warriors' Fortress. They will begin collecting it soon.
name: Displaced Energy
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Displaced Energy has started at the pond west of the Dark Warriors' Fortress!

pre_desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Bloodshed in the Wilderness has encouraged the growth of a particularly powerful evil tree it will sprout soon south of the Wilderness Crater.
name: Evil Bloodwood Tree
desc: Wilderness Flash Events: Evil Bloodwood Tree has started south of the Wilderness Crater!
